					<p class="list-level2"><span class="list-number">g.	Assignment.</span> This Agreement is entered into to secure  the  services  of Provider  and  Participating Pharmacies.   Any assignment by Provider of this Agreement or any interest hereunder shall require the prior written consent of Compliance Reward.  As used in this Agreement, the term "assignment"  shall also include a change of control in Provider or any Participating  Pharmacy, by merger,  consolidation, transfer,  or the sale  of thirty-three  percent  (33%)  or  more  stock  or  other  ownership  interest  in  Provider  or  any Participating  Pharmacy.   Any attempt  by Provider  to assign this Agreement  or its interest  hereunder without complying with the terms of this Section shall be void and of no effect, and Compliance Reward, at its option, may elect to terminate  this Agreement  without  any further liability or obligation  to Provider. Compliance Reward may assign this Agreement in whole or in part to any purchaser of all or a substantial portion of the book of business  in respect  of which this Agreement  is executed,  or to any affiliate  of Compliance Reward, provided that the assignee agrees to assume Compliance Reward's obligations under this Agreement.</p>
